snippet.title: Lemmings: Sharp X68000 (1992)
snippet.description:
Intro and gameplay from Lemmings on the Sharp X68000 system, released in 1992.
Developed by DMA Design/BANDIT and published by Psygnosis.

Game credits:
- Akira Suzuki - Music
- Brian Johnston - Music
- Dave Jones - Code
- Gary Timmons - Animation
- Scott Johnston - Graphics
- Seiji Toda - Director
- Tim Wright - Music
- Yoshihike Kurata - Code

Watch other editions of the Lemmings game here:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLW_a1Ic-Y4n_sYe2n1OCwe0j03EOxxq3U

Enjoy the video? Remember to like, comment and subscribe to Retro Gaming TV - http://bit.ly/2N5gjMA
